    "description":  "Procedures for when a local planning authority does not propose to determine a planning application in accordance with the formal recommendation of National Highways.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [
                                        {
                                            "accessible":  false,
                                            "alternative_format_contact_email":  "webmasterdft@dft.gov.uk",
                                            "attachment_type":  "file",
                                            "content_type":  "application/pdf",
                                            "file_size":  126115,
                                            "filename":  "the-town-and-country-planning-development-affecting-trunk-roads-direction-2018.pdf",
